      Changes:
      - Install now extracts into the package 'tools' directory and relies on Chocolatey shims (no PATH edits).
      - Uninstall/upgrade performs best-effort migration cleanup of legacy installs (removes old PATH entry, deletes LGPO.exe, optional LGPO_30 dir, prunes empty folders).
