    <tags>lgpo windows security gpo portable cli policy shim</tags>
    <summary>LGPO.exe is a command-line utility to automate management of Local Group Policy.</summary>
    <description>
LGPO.exe is a command-line utility that helps automate management of Local Group Policy. It can import and apply settings from Registry Policy (Registry.pol) files, security templates, Advanced Auditing backup files, and formatted "LGPO text" files; export local policy to a GPO backup; export Registry Policy contents to editable LGPO text; and build a Registry Policy file from LGPO text.
    </description>
